<br>
I personally found suspend companion 1 insuffient. I did use it once for an emergency pet in PoJ trials. One thing to keep in mind is suspend 1 is 5 points, but level 2 is only 3 more points, and the difference is so big you might (like me) find yourself powerleveling to get those last 3 aa. You won't spend very much time stuck with suspend 1 if you leveled to 64 first.<br>
<br>
Also let me amend my suggestion list a bit: if you raid alot you should get pet discipline first imho.<br>
<br>
HoE is a little more fun than suspend companion, but <br>
 So:<br>
<br>
1. Addicted to pet cannabilization: suspend companion<br>
2. Raid alot: pet hold<br>
3. Otherwise: mend companion or HoE <p>Master Cydmab Promethean<br>
